{"tid":1589241,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屯門牛同我入來！聽日(924)何妖好有可能係市政大樓出現！","createTime":"2019-09-23T08:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:27:27.000Z","uid":30138,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"39ce6070560a20078b364baad2784d3eff01ec11","tid":1589241,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:00:37.000Z","msg":"何君堯係樂翠區議員，聽日9月24（星期二）早上9：30，係屯門政府合署會有今屆屯門區議會最後一次大會，佢係區議員，suppose就要蒲頭既。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然冇人知佢會唔會出現，但就算佢唔出現， 我哋都可以對屯門區議會嗰啲建制狗抗議。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個就係圍佢老母好時機，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位手足，係時間出手了，let's go let's go rock n roll<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<br />\n日期：924（聽日！）<br />\n時間：早上9：30（但要早D去，因為一定有好多藍絲到場，好似得三十個位，一定要早過班垃圾）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地點：屯門政府合署三樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77212c210a222e3640e1116e7009562ae20021ab","tid":1589241,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:00:59.000Z","msg":"圍佢老母"},{"pid":"f151c1e52e05a2d518a56a56685ec3c8336cc3da","tid":1589241,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target